overrideManual:
access-mode=full
enable-keyboard=Y
enable-clipboard=Y
enable-file-transfer=Y
enable-camera=Y
enable-terminal=Y
enable-remote-printer=Y
enable-audio=Y
enable-tunnel=Y
enable-remote-restart=Y
enable-record-session=Y
enable-block-input=Y
allow-remote-config-modification=Y
enable-lan-discovery=Y
direct-server=Y
direct-access-port=21118
allow-auto-disconnect=N
auto-disconnect-timeout=1000
allow-only-conn-window-open=N
approve-mode=password
verification-method=use-permanent-password
theme=dark
allow-auto-record-incoming=N
allow-auto-record-outgoing=N
enable-abr=Y
